data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET at no fault of the seller. What makes this 3 bedroom fixer-upper special is the potential it holds. With some vision and effort, you can turn this property into a beautiful, custom home that suits your tastes and needs. The large amount of land offers opportunities for gardening, farming, or simply enjoying the outdoors in your own private oasis.  The combination of the barn, carport, and mature pecan tree adds to the uniqueness and potential of this fixer-upper property. With your vision and renovation efforts, you can turn these elements into valuable assets that contribute to the overall charm and functionality of your dream home.
